<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>715</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 shén a yǒu shéi néng zǔ dǎng nǐ de zhǐ yì? nǐ de zhǐ yì tōng xíng zài quán de.
 de qiú de zhǔ zǎi, zào wù de shàng dì, nǐ cì gěi lèi qì xī.
 cóng zhè jí dào nà jí, wǒ men kuài pǎo chuán yáng nǐ.
 zài zhè ēn huì de xǐ nián lǐ, bào gào shì fàng de hǎo xìn xī.
 wǒ men yào chéng wèi zàn měi de lè qì, suǒ liàn tuō luò jí bìng dōu yuǎn lí.
 zài zhè ēn huì de xǐ nián lǐ, jiù zhǔ yào lái shì fàng nǐ.</lyrics>
<title>shén a yǒu shéi néng zǔ dǎng 迦南715</title>
</song>